    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Fine linen of very light weight and slightly translucent. It is so-named for its use in making handkerchiefs, although it is also used for blouses, skirts, lingerie, children's clothing, and for other purposes as well.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
